reusable_text_info.text: DAY 2: TRYING TO MAKE $300,000 IN 30 DAYS

caption.text: Like a magnifying glass concentrating the sun’s energy so much that it can start a fire, you must concentrate your efforts to succeed big. It’s why I make my Viral Video Bootcamp short but INTENSE. It will stretch you and push you, like a magnifying glass for your efforts. And you’ll come out with more knowledge and momentum in 6 weeks than you’d get in a year plodding along alone. If you want to be the first to hear about it, comment WAITLIST and you’ll get first dibs on one of the 60 spots

caption.text:
Social media changes so fast it’ll make your spin. It’s why so many creators have flash in the pan success. So how do you win a game that shifts under mental your feet? I have 2 core strategies: 

1) learn the fundamentals of storytelling, psychology and marketing. Platforms change fast but people change very, very slowly. Understand them, and you will win over the long term. 

2) learn to control your mind. A weak mind will never have staying power. Self sabotage, limiting beliefs, procrastination, fear, impatience - these things all stem from the same place. And they all guarantee you’ll struggle. Get your mind right, and the outcomes will take care of themselves. I know this sounds woo-woo. For the first part of my journey, I ignored this. And do you know what it lead to? Anxiety, demotivation, a repulsion for content creation and eventually burnout. It’s the biggest unlock I have with the creators I work with. 

If you want me to work with you on these things. If you want guidance from someone who has walked the walk - with almost 1 million followers across platforms in just 23 months. Then comment WAITLIST and I’ll tell you all about it, plus you’ll get first dibs on the limited spots

#instagramgrowth #socialmediamarketing
